<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title></title>
</head>

<body>
  <h1>Hi, welcome to Rock Paper Scissors</h1>
  <p>What is your name? (Single player) </p>
  <form action="/game" method="post">
    <p>Player 1: <input id="player1-name-textbox" type="text" name="player1"></p>
    <p>Do you want to use lizard spock options too?</p>
    <input type="checkbox" id="gametype" name="gametype" value="5">
    <label for="gametype"> Yes! </label><br>
    <input id="names-submit" type="submit" value="Submit!">
  </form>
  <p>Or enter names here for multiplayer!</p>
  <form action="/gameMulti" method="post">
    <p>Player 1: <input id="player1-name-textbox" type="text" name="player1"></p>
    <p>Player 2: <input id="player2-name-textbox" type="text" name="player2"></p>
    <p>Do you want to use lizard spock options too?</p>
    <input type="checkbox" id="gametype" name="gametype" value="5">
    <label for="gametype"> Yes! </label><br>
    <input id="names-submit" type="submit" value="Submit!">
  </form>

</body>

</html>